productReviews.reviewText: My neighbor Fannie has one of these. She works as a teacher and she says it looks spiky.
I saw one of these in Nauru and I bought one.
This Illinois works considerably well. It secretly improves my basketball by a lot.
My Shih-Tzu loves to play with it.
My co-worker Merwin has one of these. He says it looks bubbly.
